snippet.title: Propagation: Paradise Hotel - Official Reveal Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2021
snippet.description:
Here's a creepy tease for Propagation: Paradise Hotel, an upcoming survival horror adventure game sequel to the 2020 zombie shooter, Propagation VR. 

Propagation: Paradise Hotel is coming in late 2022 with plans for the game to be available on all major VR platforms.

#IGN #Gaming
